    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I have treated this car like my absolute baby, and it shows\u2014it's in truly pristine, showroom-ready condition. It\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and honestly looks like it just rolled off the lot for the first time. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and drives like a dream, this is the one! I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
