      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute gem! I\u2019ve taken such good care of this car, it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's in stunning condition, inside and out\u2014seriously, it\u2019s been totally babied. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
